Interface Copyable

  • All Known Subinterfaces:
    Linkable, Rotation
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    BogusEvent, ButtonShortcut, Camera, ClickEvent, ClickProfile, ClickShortcut, DOF1Event, DOF2Event, DOF3Event, DOF6Event, Eye, Frame, InteractiveAvatarFrame, InteractiveEyeFrame, InteractiveFrame, KeyboardEvent, KeyboardProfile, KeyboardShortcut, KeyFrameInterpolator, Mat, MotionEvent, MotionProfile, Profile, Quat, Rot, Shortcut, Vec, Window

    public interface Copyable
    Interface for returning a deep copy on the object.

    The pattern to perform a deep copy on an object using this Interface comprises a two-step process:

    1. Declare/implement a protected copy constructor protected Object(Object otherObject).
    2. Override get() by invoking the protected constructor return new Object(this).
